{
  "stem": "20088.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one, once was-- was a British prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when she wanted to change something on her clothes, he went outside.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She said, he was still a gentleman, you know?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was quite typical.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They all just were all [INAUDIBLE] had forgotten that the man would go out if a woman wants to do, you know, something, like we were all quite open.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But said make a great impression on her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so somehow, she must have been able to get information where this transport from Auschwitz had gone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they knew it had gone to [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Czernowitz. ?] And they put her, then, eventually on a train what was going to go there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So and when she came to me, instead of cuddling her and kissing her, I was very close with her.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I shouted at her, how could you have done that to me and to leave me again?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, I was very, very cross with her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she was very upset with me that I-- it just wasn't her fault.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So-- but anyway, we were reunited.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then I said, and you must never leave my side anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so we went on and on east, southeast and till eventually, we ended up in Odessa.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that's where they said they were going to leave us till the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we can go back by boat to the West.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put us up in a beautiful old palace.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing was in it, but you can still see lovely rooms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Again, it was in a-- in a-- on the floor we had to sleep.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was a big park.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And in this park, all kind of groups had been put.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
